&lt;h2 id=&#34;3将幻灯片1复制&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#3将幻灯片1复制&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 3. 将幻灯片 1 复制&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://imgconvert.csdnimg.cn/aHR0cHM6Ly9waWMzLnpoaW1nLmNvbS84MC92Mi0yZDVhYjU5YTkwM2Q4ZGRjMTRmNDg4Y2QzNWIyYmU0YV8xNDQwdy5qcGc?x-oss-process=image/format,png#pic_center&#34; alt=&#34;在这里插入图片描述&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
